Text:
I've already written this answer in the upload where you asked it, I write it there as it's probable you can read it earlier here... :-)

If you open the SFX file with WinRAR, and click on the "Comment" icon of the WinRAR Toolbar, you can modify the Command list. You can modify it also during the SFX creation, but I regularly forget to do it, so I modify it later...;-)
